/**
 * ============================================================================
 * EUREKA DISCOVERY SERVER
 * ============================================================================
 * 
 * What is Eureka Discovery Server?
 * - Service registry for microservices
 * - Services register themselves with Eureka
 * - Clients discover services through Eureka
 * - Provides load balancing capabilities
 * - Enables service resilience
 * 
 * How it Works:
 * 1. Services register with Eureka on startup
 * 2. Eureka maintains registry of all services
 * 3. Services send heartbeats to stay registered
 * 4. Clients query Eureka to find services
 * 5. Eureka removes unresponsive services
 * 
 * Port: 8761
 * ============================================================================
 */

